      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Work on the line into Rosalia\nhas practically been completed with\nthe exception of ballasting, the ex-\nIRENE cold making it impossible to\ncontinue this work, but we hope to\nopen train service to Rosalia in a\nweek or ten days\" p\n\n\nThe Spokane & Inland is now\nequipped with Is handsome Brill\ncoaches and with the order about\nto be placed will have a total OF\n80. They will all be needed as soon\nas the road opens to Colfax and\nPalouse.\n\n\nThe road now has so box cars\nand 20 fiat cars and will have q\ntotal freight equipment, when tho\nadditional cars ordered arrive, 0x\n$50 cars."
